WEBVTT

00:05.005 --> 00:07.007
[whinnying]

00:11.469 --> 00:13.471
[horse chuffs]

00:15.015 --> 00:16.349
[theme music playing]

00:16.433 --> 00:18.184
♪ I'm gonna ride ♪

00:18.268 --> 00:20.228
♪ I'm riding free ♪

00:20.311 --> 00:22.272
♪ So come along, let's go along ♪

00:22.355 --> 00:24.399
♪ Come on the journey with me ♪

00:24.482 --> 00:26.317
♪ I'm gonna ride ♪

00:26.401 --> 00:28.403
♪ I'm riding free ♪

00:28.486 --> 00:30.530
♪ As long as I am here with you ♪

00:30.613 --> 00:32.741
♪ I feel the spirit within me ♪

00:32.824 --> 00:34.868
-♪ Yeah, eh, eh ♪
-♪ Yeah, eh, eh, eh ♪

00:34.951 --> 00:36.953
-♪ Yeah, eh, eh ♪
-♪ Yeah, eh, eh, eh ♪

